Zotero,is,a,free,tool,to,help,users,collect,organize,cite,and,share,their,research,sources,It,is,implemented,as,an,extension,for,the,Firefox,browser,The,API,provides,some,of,the,functionality,of,the,plugin,including,retrieval,of,tags,user,specific,items,collections,and,subcollections,The,API,uses,both,REST,and,JavaScript,protocol,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML,and,XHTML